  "text": "We further defined a sub-set of PRs whose distances were known from the literature. The knowledge of the distance allows us to perform a volumetric analysis of the environment, similar to that made for other kinds of peculiar galaxies [CITATION_1] , Heckman et al. 1985 , Hintzen et al. 1991 . Unfortunately, most PRs lack known red-shift, and the 'volume' sub-set is so restricted to 31 galaxies.",
